title: Solas  -  2 albums
description:
Here we have two great quality albums by an amazing band, Solas.

waiting for  an echo
The Edge of Silence


They are an Irish-American band, playing almost-but-not-quite traditional irish folk music.
If you have not heard of them, I guarantee you they are great.  If you have heard of them, then you're welcome. I'm sure you are happy to see this finally uploaded.


Enjoy.
